title: Prank War Leaks His Phone Number
itunes:author: Joe Vulpis & Ilya Feddy
description:
Leaking his phone number to 200,000 people, performing at the biggest festivals in the world, and creating songs for massive movies, Dillon Francis is no stranger to the music scene. Our friend Dillon Francis comes by Lightweights Podcast to talk about his new song dropping today, performing at Coachella 4 years, and his epic prank war with DJ Snake.


Check out Dillon on instagram here: https://www.instagram.com/dillonfrancis/


Watch our FULL Video Podcast on Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCjmqbxZsoH1YwihrGgU1vPA
